long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
🏆Best tool made for people who want to export Facebook group members into CSV.

A brilliant members export tool that allows you to quickly export Facebook group members to CSV with just one click!

🖖  KEY FEATURES:

Export FB group members with one click.

🚗 DESCRIPTION Step by Step:

1.Click the export button.

⛵️ SUPPORTED COLUMNS:

user id
username
is verified
friendship status
group bio
join group time
profile url

🔎  HOW DOES IT WORK:

Using Facebook's official API to export data.
Free user can export the first 200 records.
Paid users can export without limits. Only $9.9!

🔒  USAGE POLICY

No password required.
All the data you export is processed locally, so no one knows what you exported.
